                Mr. Brendan Bracken  (Bournemouth)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1af4d814-d478-4af7-a2fe-ccfab4bd2e76" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
