<p class="">Is it not a fact that we saw millions of Indians starve previously, when we were in India?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-5b8bc663-f835-465e-afae-172ef520624e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
