                Mr. Raikes
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a0fb1be1-1204-4472-8cf0-dedd4b91dec0" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-11-05/debates/b1170b18-5d77-4364-ba97-4a573172c43e/BurmaIndependenceBill#contribution-a0fb1be1-1204-4472-8cf0-dedd4b91dec0">
