            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-59c77eb6-56f6-44f5-8e68-ed7a3202e553" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
