    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">In the past—going back into history again—were not the English, the Scots, the Welsh and the Irish divided, and have they not been fused into one political whole? Could not that happen in Burma as well?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
