    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">What has Marshal Badoglio got to do with Burma?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f27fb084-5ce5-4e6a-8cf9-b711ba71ae87" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
